{"tid":1666906,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[為所欲為] 華為mate30被指動態降低遊戲解析度，遊戲性能測試數據全部作廢","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T13:50:36.000Z","uid":109923,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"24b39f3bb818440307ff0bfbad938869c5f58cca","tid":1666906,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"最近，一名叫做歐陽秋葉的科技數碼blogger表示，自己在測試遊戲的時候，發現華為mate30手機在同等畫質下的解析度有所降低，而且降低解析度的條件不固定，因此這次測試華為mate30遊戲性能的數據不得已全部作廢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6h3daOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6h3daOQ.jpg&h=7762e367&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n華為最新mate30被指強制降低遊戲解析度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0pTaY2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0pTaY2.png&h=ef4ac530&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n左邊華為Mate30的遊戲畫面，右邊的是黑鯊手機的畫面，肉眼對比擷圖可以發現，華為Mate30手機的遊戲畫面較模糊。後續透過多擷圖放大對比，大致可以確定華為Mate30手機把1080P降低至720P顯示。<br />\n<br />\n有中國用家指出，即使關閉性能模式和開啟固定解析度也無法禁止華為閹割畫質<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WoEDm8g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWoEDm8g.png&h=e6e93cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbASrnO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbASrnO.png&h=f705073f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uucmjKc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuucmjKc.png&h=e1de6585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5m6vSt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5m6vSt.png&h=29f90843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦有人指出華為造假早有先例，今年年初，華為旗艦 P30 Pro 更是號稱搭載全球最強後置鏡頭，但自發布以來 P30 Pro 的拍月亮功能卻飽受外界爭議。有媒體認為華為P30 手機的拍月亮功能存在造假。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsGBS64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsGBS64.png&h=9c2dd97a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QANJx6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQANJx6G.jpg&h=f9f94458&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n中國評測媒體愛否科技的科技編輯@王躍琨 的看法引起外界激烈討論，因為華為P30 Pro 不僅能拍攝到月亮的全景，甚至連月球上面的一些細節都能顯示的一清二楚，例如月球上的「環形坑」，這種鏡頭已經不僅能堪比單反，還能跟望遠鏡一決高下。但在隨後的測試中，華為P30 Pro 被證實自動拍月亮是使用了 AI 算法，並非是像單反那樣直接拍成的<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PeUjQTm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPeUjQTm.jpg&h=454cbdce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於此次強制降解析度，華為如何解畫？<br />\n華為高管李小龍回應：這是bug<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TVZQ0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TVZQ0q.png&h=e34e28c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEOMvVQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEOMvVQ.png&h=427a5bc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e9c7f6c400cf292751a12f1c43e02785a676c3c","tid":1666906,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda9177bad89fd7f1a7d9352167bdc7d6cd25429","tid":1666906,"uid":322622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:38:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93e65e84f89b8c3225bc749b4d5774095e181c82","tid":1666906,"uid":163493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"支那"},{"pid":"8ff927b230ed6b0f4d419087e00210d65b89776c","tid":1666906,"uid":109923,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"華為美麗嘅手機UI<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMCJxSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMCJxSo.jpg&h=40a894dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br 